    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Describes videotape 8mm in width, used primarily for home use in hand-held cameras or camcorders. The resolution quality for 8mm videotape is 240 lines.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000047993/Konigsberg, The Complete Film Dictionary (1987)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Describe cintas de video de 8mm de ancho, usadas principalmente para uso doméstico en cámaras manuales o cámaras de video y audio. La calidad de resolución para cintas de 8mm es de 240 lineas.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
